<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><img alt="Massad Is Confirmed as Chairman of Futures Commission" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/06/04/business/dbpix-massad/dbpix-massad-square320.jpg" width="75" height="75" border="0" /><span class="title">Massad Is Confirmed as Chairman of Futures Commission <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> The Senate confirmed Timothy G. Massad as well as two other commissioners, Sharon Y. Bowen and J. Christopher Giancarlo. <span class="elsewhere"><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/06/03/massad-is-confirmed-as-chairman-of-futures-commission/">DealBook Â»</a></span></p>
